                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2137" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0330</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8632 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">麦德龙郑州商场：大型商超粉丝营销急先锋</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The “Doing”, “Communicating” and “Linking” of the Fans Operation of Metro Mall in Zhengzhou</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">周修亭，张孟文等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑州大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">麦德龙集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">麦德龙郑州商场；粉丝营销；微营销；微品牌</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Zhengzhou Metro Mall; fans marketing; micro marketing;  micro brand</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">特立独行的会员制销售模式一度让麦德龙集团（超市）成为世界第二、欧洲第一的商业集团，其在中国的发展也很成功。这一模式的关键在于发展和稳定相当规模的客户，在当今互联网思维和微营销的背景下，传统的做法正在遭遇不同程度的挑战，如何有效的利用新媒体与客户互动沟通，增加粉丝数量和粉丝黏度，利用好粉丝渠道，提升粉丝转化率，也就是持续开发和长期稳定会员客户成为重中之重。麦德龙郑州商场大胆创新，推出了逆向营销、知识营销、增值服务、用活粉丝渠道、软文营销、异业联盟与跨界营销、微品牌等一系列实操性很强的微营销策略，同时也克服了单纯性的粉丝营销的弊端，为传统连锁型商业企业营销转型提供了有益的借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The maverick membership sales model once made METRO Group (supermarket) the world’s number two and the European’s number one business group. It also has a believable successful development in China, in which the key to its model is to develop and keep a mass of stable and loyal customers. The traditional sales models are taking varying degrees of challenge under the background of the internet thinking and micro marketing today. It becomes very important that how effectively to use new media to interact with customers, increase the number of fans and its viscosity, make good use of fans channels and enhance the conversion rate of the fans. In other words, the continued development and long-term stability of member-customers have become a priority. Metro mall in Zhengzhou innovates boldly and proposes a series of fairly practical micro-marketing strategies, such as reverse marketing, knowledge marketing, value-added services, effective arrangement of fans channels, article marketing, horizontal alliances and crossover marketing, micro brand and so on. It also overcomes the drawbacks of simple fans marketing and provides a useful reference for the marketing transition of the traditional chain-type commercial enterprise.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销管理》、《服务市场营销》、《营销管理案例分析》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">微营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015-09</td>
                            </tr>
